1.  Go to semantic-ui folder,
2.  # npm i
3.  # gulp
4.  Config files will be created.

> Disable Google fonts:

    1.  Go to file: /src/site/globals/site.variables
    2.  Add: @importGoogleFonts : false;
    3.  # gulp build

> Activate RTL components:

    1.  Go to file: /semantic.json
    2.  Change rtl to true.
